{"tid":650682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日發夢？","createTime":"2018-05-02T14:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T00:06:26.000Z","uid":1653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cea608ea81ee0a919d895af3bafb6d69a723dfa","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"幾乎每晚都會發夢<br />\n全部都係惡夢 夢入面好驚、好恐懼、好無助<br />\n驚到醒咗 訓返又會繼續嗰個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒咗都會心慌慌一段時間<br />\n有時會記得些少片段 有時會記得晒成個夢<br />\n多數都係俾人跟蹤 追殺<br />\n間唔時係關於喪屍 末日 逃亡<br />\n好多夢嘅背景係以前住嘅舊屋 去過嘅地方 或者半真實半假嘅場景<br />\n我冇睇開有關喪屍 末日呢類嘅戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講成日發被追嘅夢係壓力大<br />\n但我覺得自己壓力未至於大到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過瞓前做下運動 聽下輕鬆嘅音樂 放鬆心情<br />\n但都係冇改善<br />\n晚晚冇覺好瞓 搞到個人瞓覺好似冇瞓過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命啊好想瞓餐好覺啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b26adcc09bebef91550cd4377bad453595e51c6","tid":650682,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"前兩日發過個喪屍夢，幾過癮"},{"pid":"d4e7ce3517c8e1a043ea43b8cae0c5ff2e6b3d5a","tid":650682,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"我都成日發夢<br />\n一係比人追殺，一係冇著衫"},{"pid":"3f7775390717d7c5593e94afca8182fa0a8d600f","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b26adcc09bebef91550cd4377bad453595e51c6","tid":650682,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"前兩日發過個喪屍夢，幾過癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"琴晚又發完黎啊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚇撚到我鳩縮<br />\n如果第時真係有喪屍我應該會有好高嘅生存能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47eba5ebd1bb621263f2a5a29c98a3b5725a459c","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"成日夢見男朋友"},{"pid":"9d96dd56738663fc3d67cba8e7b77743afafd5a9","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4e7ce3517c8e1a043ea43b8cae0c5ff2e6b3d5a","tid":650682,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"我都成日發夢<br />\n一係比人追殺，一係冇著衫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"試過一次冇著衫嘅夢....<br />\n係有個男人跟住我行旋轉樓梯 每次望後佢都用好陰森嘅眼神望住我<br />\n然後轉個畫面唔知做乜俾佢捉住咗 兩個打大赤肋 俾佢屌埋 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1167e896117af3e0df87b922bae09bb4f48a1c","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47eba5ebd1bb621263f2a5a29c98a3b5725a459c","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"成日夢見男朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"係咪好sweet 我都好想夢見我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何發埋啲咁嘅鳩夢"},{"pid":"d7fc89d52b874b5c71fbb2003b72eef8d92377e7","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1167e896117af3e0df87b922bae09bb4f48a1c","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47eba5ebd1bb621263f2a5a29c98a3b5725a459c","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"成日夢見男朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"係咪好sweet 我都好想夢見我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何發埋啲咁嘅鳩夢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通係我夢到出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都成日發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有同一個場地會夢見好多次"},{"pid":"99e84f0263ae5cb6c78a66fb593d93d208fbdfab","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fc89d52b874b5c71fbb2003b72eef8d92377e7","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1167e896117af3e0df87b922bae09bb4f48a1c","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47eba5ebd1bb621263f2a5a29c98a3b5725a459c","tid":650682,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"成日夢見男朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"係咪好sweet 我都好想夢見我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何發埋啲咁嘅鳩夢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通係我夢到出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都成日發惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有同一個場地會夢見好多次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"我都會啊<br />\n重好似劇集咁有連接返上個夢嘅故仔添<br />\n有次因爲同一個場景 意識到自己發緊夢 所以控制咗個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debfc93f07d77def73a1d6fbdfa7372e9c05c7b2","tid":650682,"uid":34806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"我成日發幾類夢<br />\n第一類係雙膝無力 場場多數踢波或者跑步<br />\n個人好難企成身 屁股貼地咁踢波   好似狗咁四足跑步<br />\n<br />\n第二類係下體裸露 場境係學校 多數係裸住完早會走樓梯上班房的場境<br />\n<br />\n第三煩係俾人追殺類 呢煩就追殺你果個永遠追你唔到 但我又永遠擺脫唔到佢 多數係俾怪物同菲利追<br />\n場景有河道都公屋後樓梯<br />\n<br />\n第四類就係知道已經發過呢個夢類 即係你一開波就Feel 到自己經歷過 下一刻會發生咩都知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢4 類比較常見<br />\n<br />\n間唔中會有甩牙類"},{"pid":"31c51f75669eab9276587cbe4f16c2a8ebdb95c0","tid":650682,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffcda3eacccb57c768ad8651b15d35663f6eb4a6","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"究竟發夢係咪真係反映緊d野？<br />\n係咪有野可以解釋出黎？<br />\n有冇人答到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc1d138812ac9eef869128fa72ca7c7f8317b8b","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"debfc93f07d77def73a1d6fbdfa7372e9c05c7b2","tid":650682,"uid":34806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"我成日發幾類夢<br />\n第一類係雙膝無力 場場多數踢波或者跑步<br />\n個人好難企成身 屁股貼地咁踢波   好似狗咁四足跑步<br />\n<br />\n第二類係下體裸露 場境係學校 多數係裸住完早會走樓梯上班房的場境<br />\n<br />\n第三煩係俾人追殺類 呢煩就追殺你果個永遠追你唔到 但我又永遠擺脫唔到佢 多數係俾怪物同菲利追<br />\n場景有河道都公屋後樓梯<br />\n<br />\n第四類就係知道已經發過呢個夢類 即係你一開波就Feel 到自己經歷過 下一刻會發生咩都知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢4 類比較常見<br />\n<br />\n間唔中會有甩牙類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"第三類我成日發<br />\n不斷搵路走 好撚無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n甩牙試過一次 啲牙重變晒做石仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6023d0b1e40405f076760ae06c38ce26c45416d7","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31c51f75669eab9276587cbe4f16c2a8ebdb95c0","tid":650682,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d96dd56738663fc3d67cba8e7b77743afafd5a9","tid":650682,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4e7ce3517c8e1a043ea43b8cae0c5ff2e6b3d5a","tid":650682,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"我都成日發夢<br />\n一係比人追殺，一係冇著衫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"試過一次冇著衫嘅夢....<br />\n係有個男人跟住我行旋轉樓梯 每次望後佢都用好陰森嘅眼神望住我<br />\n然後轉個畫面唔知做乜俾佢捉住咗 兩個打大赤肋 俾佢屌埋 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"屌 我想架咩<br />\n我都想力保後門 但醒唔到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\